David Palmer DEWBERRY, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-1997 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

REVERSED. REMANDED.
